metadata.name: World Data Miners #1
metadata.description: The World Data Miner NFT Collection is 10,000 unique, hand drawn Miners from across space and time, spanning earth years 1977-3077, and immortalized forever on the Ethereum Blockchain. WDM a decentralized, members-only organization helping our members build passive revenue streams using the data already being collected on us. These NFTs serve as ownership in World Data DAO and entitle the holder to a bevy of benefits. Visit worlddataminer.com for details.
